sentences: Yoo Ki-hyun (Korean: 유기현; born November 22, 1993), better known mononymously as Kihyun, is a South Korean singer.
He is a vocalist in the South Korean boy group Monsta X, which debuted under Starship Entertainment in 2015 through Mnet's survival show
Kihyun was born on November 22, 1993 in Seoul, South Korea.
